1. Decide which business to order pizza from.
2. Decide which of the business' locations to order from.
3. Pull up the menu.
4. Decide which type of pizza to order from the menu.
5. Customize pizzas by adding or removing toppings from your desired pizza on the menu.
6. Decide the quantity of each previously selected type of pizza to order.
7. Decide how the pizzas will be recieved (delivery or pickup)
8. Decide how the pizzas will be paid for.
9. Submit a request to the business location based on information from steps 1-8.
10. Await delivery OR travel to pickup location (dependant on step 7)
11. Accept Pizza(s)